close_reason: "Regression suite, temp-dir dogfood, release gates, security scan, and Sentry/telemetry checks all passed for init guidance delivery."
body: "Focused coverage plan:\n- tests/unit/init-command.spec.ts: helper-level present/missing/outdated detection, writer idempotence, AGENTS-only, CLAUDE-only, both files, absent files, and TTY-decline/add state transitions.\n- tests/unit/settings-store.spec.ts: agent_guidance defaults, schema migration from missing state, deterministic serialization key order, and persistence of declined metadata.\n- tests/unit/config-command.spec.ts if config key is added: inspect/reset behavior and settings write op.\n- tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts and tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts: init flag/help/contract visibility.\n- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts: JSON key ordering for any new init result field, non-interactive init does not hang, and explicit add/status behavior works in a temp repository.\n- Use node scripts/run-tests.mjs so PM_PATH and PM_GLOBAL_PATH remain sandboxed."
